###Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "maddy",
  "email": "maddy@test.com",
  "password": "123456"

  
}

### Login User
  ##Returns JWT Token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maddy@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}


